00:01:47,633 --> 00:01:51,025
Shah Jahan was born on 5th January 1592,

38
00:01:51,025 --> 00:01:52,691
his real name was Khurram.

39
00:01:52,691 --> 00:01:54,746
Shah Jahan, was the royal name

40
00:01:54,746 --> 00:01:56,309
which was bestowed on him later,

41
00:01:56,309 --> 00:01:57,725
literally meaning 'the King of the World'.

42
00:01:57,725 --> 00:01:58,816
Shah Jahan.

43
00:01:58,816 --> 00:02:02,093
His father was Jahangir and
his mother was Jagat Gosain.

44
00:02:02,093 --> 00:02:04,127
The chief queen of Jahangir.

45
00:02:04,127 --> 00:02:07,924
Mumtaz Mahal was born in 1593.

46
00:02:07,924 --> 00:02:11,649
The name Mumtaz Mahal was bestowed on her after her wedding.

47
00:02:11,649 --> 00:02:14,523
