103
00:04:43,232 --> 00:04:45,799
The white marble was brought in from Rajasthan,

104
00:04:45,799 --> 00:04:47,166
Jasper from Punjab,

105
00:04:47,166 --> 00:04:49,130
Jade and Crystal from China,

106
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:50,512
Turquoise from Tibet,

107
00:04:50,512 --> 00:04:51,966
Sapphire from Sri Lanka,

108
00:04:51,966 --> 00:04:53,997
And Carnelian from Arabia.

109
00:04:53,997 --> 00:04:57,091
The gems and materials that can be found in the Taj Mahal,

110
00:04:57,091 --> 00:04:58,557
have come from all over the world.

