449
00:20:20,485 --> 00:20:22,090
Waiting in the queue for his turn.

450
00:20:22,090 --> 00:20:24,009
As soon as they would have started cutting off their hands,

451
00:20:24,009 --> 00:20:25,314
the others would have run away.

